All Classes

  • Class Description
    ChangeListener
    Represents a listener that subscribes to the changes of Observable
    ListenerEntry
    Internal data class holding listener reference together with its priority.
    ListenerNotification
    Observable listener notification method
    ListenerPriority
    A utility enum defining five levels of ChangeListener priority
    Observable
    Base Observable class that holds a list of listeners and notifies them when it changes.
    SettableObservable<T extends Observable>
    Maintains a set of observable listeners and parents for settable property
    SettableProperty<T>
    A wrapper class that encapsulates another object - modelValue - and notifies it's listeners when the modelValue is set.
